<p>Ok, moment of truth! Run the test!</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/phpunit -c app --filter testGETProgrammer</div></code></pre>
<p>And... it's failing. Ah, the URL has <code>?nickname=UnitTester</code>. Woh woh. I bet that's
my fault. The name of the route in <code>onPostSerialize()</code> should be  <code>api_programmers_show</code>:</p>
