<p>Re-run the test:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/phpunit -c app --filter testGETProgrammer</div></code></pre>
<p>It's still failing, but for a new reason. This time it doesn't like the <code>app_test.php</code>
at the beginning of the link URI. Where's that coming from?</p>
<p>The test class extends an <code>ApiTestCase</code>: we made this in an earlier episode. This
app already has a <code>test</code> environment and it configures a <em>test</em> database connection.
If we can force every URL through <code>app_test.php</code>, it'll use that test database, and
we'll be really happy:</p>
